><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1108036" src="https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/【VShojoNext】-Im-here-VShojo-_-kson-Official-VSHOJO-Lore-7-47-screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/【VShojoNext】-Im-here-VShojo-_-kson-Official-VSHOJO-Lore-7-47-screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/【VShojoNext】-Im-here-VShojo-_-kson-Official-VSHOJO-Lore-7-47-screenshot-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/【VShojoNext】-Im-here-VShojo-_-kson-Official-VSHOJO-Lore-7-47-screenshot-768x432.jpg 768w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/【VShojoNext】-Im-here-VShojo-_-kson-Official-VSHOJO-Lore-7-47-screenshot-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/【VShojoNext】-Im-here-VShojo-_-kson-Official-VSHOJO-Lore-7-47-screenshot.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>有網民指今次 VShojo 是黑船來襲進軍日本，發掘日本市場就請來了擁有 121 萬名訂閱者的 Kson，以及背後是一把非常熟悉的聲音的新人「飴宮なずな」（Amemiya Nazuna）。根據官網所示，Kson 將以其一向的人設加入 Vshojo，而飴宮なずな則是一個患失憶症的少女，拿著一把巨大的鑰匙，她相信自己是一名天使，但詳細已經記不清了。她思考敏銳，並喜愛閱讀。在 Kson 頻道所載的影片中，可清楚聽到她的聲音。根據直播透露，Kson 與，飴宮なずな 會在 7 月 16 日正式在 VShojo 出道。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-03-上午 4.34.24-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1108035" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-03-上午 4.34.24-694x506.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="506" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-03-上午 4.34.24-694x506.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-03-上午 4.34.24-1233x900.jpg 1233w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-03-上午 4.34.24-768x560.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-03-上午 4.34.24-1536x1121.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-03-上午 4.34.24-2048x1495.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-03-上午 4.36.39-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1108038" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-03-上午 4.36.39-694x507.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="507" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-03-上午 4.36.39-694x507.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-03-上午 4.36.39-1232x900.jpg 1232w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-03-上午 4.36.39-768x561.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-03-上午 4.36.39-1536x1122.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-03-上午 4.36.39-2048x1496.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>VTuber 企業在日本除了已獲得成功的 Cover（Hololive）之外，Anycolor （にじさんじ，中譯彩虹社）早前上市後股價升勢強勁，總市值曾升破 1600 億日元（約港幣 91.7 億元）。而美國 VTuber 公司 VShojo 在今年 3 月宣佈完成了 1,100 萬美元（約港幣 8,632 萬元）的種子輪融資，將進一步發展 VTuber 娛樂事業。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_82827"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/NQlH1lXq4tg?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.vshojo.com/talent">Vshojo</a>, <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NQlH1lXq4tg">YouTube</a></p><h2> 最新影片</